## Description: 
## 		method of creating linux system-daemon


# step 1: 
	copy All Folder "createSystemDaemon" to Device-Under-Test (in OS) 

# step 2: 
	do "sudo su" or "su root"

# step 3: 
	review & configurate "createSystemDaemon.sh"

# step 4: 
	excute "createSystemDaemon.sh"

# caution: 
	if you want to check status linux system-daemon "rc-local.service",
	do command:
		"systemctl status rc-local.service"
	;
	or if you want to stop linux system-daemon "rc-local.service",
	do command:
		"systemctl disable rc-local.service""
